            repository_id,
            origin,
            label,
            suite,
            codename,
            description,
            contents
        ) VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6, $7)

            repository_id = $1,
            origin = $2,
            label = $3,
            suite = $4,
            codename = $5,
            description = $6,
            contents = $7
